cabal-version:       3.0
name:                cheops-logger-example
version:             0.0.1.0
synopsis:            Structured logger implementation.
description:

  Example application that uses the logger.
  
  Example is currently unbuildable, see https://github.com/cheopslab/cheops-logger/issues/4

